Task 3.2: Audit and gap-fill godot.py tests

Audit: test_godot.py already had 42 tests covering all §4.2 spec requirements.
All tests mock _is_executable rather than calling it directly, leaving line 151
uncovered.

Gap-fill: Added 3 tests calling _is_executable directly:
1. test_is_executable_nonexistent_path - returns False for missing path
2. test_is_executable_existing_file - returns True for real file
3. test_is_executable_not_executable - returns False when os.access denies

Result: godot.py coverage 99% -> 100% (55 tests, all pass)
